net.sf.mmm.util.query.base.statement

Class AbstractSelectStatement<E,SELF extends SelectStatement<E,SELF>,T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.query.base.statement.AbstractStatement<E,SELF>
      • net.sf.mmm.util.query.base.statement.AbstractSelectStatement<E,SELF,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the generic type of the queried object (typically a Bean).
    SELF - the generic type of this query itself (this) for fluent API calls.
    T - the generic type of the internal results. See getMapper().
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Command, FeatureFetch<E>, FeatureGroupBy<SELF>, FeatureLimit<SELF>, FeatureOrderBy<SELF>, FeaturePaging<SELF>, FeatureWhere<SELF>, StatementFeature, SelectStatement<E,SELF>, Statement<E,SELF>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JpqlSelectStatementImpl, OrientDbSelectStatementImpl

    public abstract class AbstractSelectStatement<E,SELF extends SelectStatement<E,SELF>,T>
extends AbstractStatement<E,SELF>
implements SelectStatement<E,SELF>
    This is the abstract base-implementation of SelectStatement.
    Since:
    8.0.0
    Author:
    hohwille
